---
// CTA .ey-cta - reconstrução fiel
---

<section class="ey-cta" aria-label="Agendar aula experimental de yoga em Sorocaba">

  <div class="ey-cta__bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="ey-cta__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="ey-cta__container">
    <div class="ey-cta__inner">

      <p class="ey-cta__eyebrow">Aula Experimental</p>

      <h2 class="ey-cta__title">
        Vamos juntos nessa caminhada de <em>evolução</em> e transformação?
      </h2>

      <p class="ey-cta__text">
        Agende sua aula experimental e descubra como o Yoga pode mudar a sua relação com o corpo, a mente e a respiração.
      </p>

      <a href="#contato" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ey-cta__btn" aria-label="Agendar aula experimental pelo WhatsApp">
        <span>Agendar Aula Experimental</span>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ey-cta {
    --green-deep: #154A30;
    --lime: #BEEBAC;
    --lilac-light: #E0A8EE;

    --font-serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Cormorant Fallback', 'Georgia', serif;
    --font-sans: 'Outfit', 'Outfit Fallback', system-ui, sans-serif;

    --fs-xs: clamp(0.68rem, 0.66rem + 0.12vw, 0.76rem);
    --fs-sm: clamp(0.82rem, 0.8rem + 0.14vw, 0.92rem);
    --fs-base: clamp(0.95rem, 0.92rem + 0.18vw, 1.05rem);
    --fs-2xl: clamp(2rem, 1.4rem + 2.4vw, 3.4rem);

    --r-pill: 999px;
    --ease: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);

    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(4rem, 3rem + 4vw, 7rem) 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #0a1f10;
    scroll-margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .ey-cta *,
  .ey-cta *::before,
  .ey-cta *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  .ey-cta__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -60px 0;
    background-image: url("/images/cta-bg.webp");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center 40%;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .ey-cta__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(10, 31, 16, 0.85) 0%,
      rgba(21, 74, 48, 0.80) 50%,
      rgba(10, 31, 16, 0.88) 100%
    );
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ey-cta__container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 1rem + 3vw, 4rem);
  }

  .ey-cta__inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ey-cta__eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #E0A8EE !important;
  }
  .ey-cta__eyebrow::before {
    content: "";
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: #E0A8EE !important;
  }

  .ey-cta__title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--fs-2xl);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #FFFFFF !important;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 1rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
  }

  .ey-cta__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #BEEBAC !important;
  }

  .ey-cta__text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--fs-base);
    color: #FFFFFF !important;
    opacity: 0.92;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
  }

  .ey-cta__btn,
  .ey-cta__btn:visited,
  .ey-cta__btn:link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    min-height: 50px;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: var(--r-pill);
    background: #FFFFFF !important;
    color: #154A30 !important;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    transition: all 400ms var(--ease);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
  }
  .ey-cta__btn:hover,
  .ey-cta__btn:focus-visible {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    background: #BEEBAC !important;
    color: #154A30 !important;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
  }
  .ey-cta__btn svg {
    width: 15px;
    height: 15px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 300ms var(--ease);
    stroke: #154A30 !important;
  }
  .ey-cta__btn:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ey-cta { padding: clamp(3rem, 2.5rem + 2vw, 4.5rem) 0; }
    .ey-cta__bg {
      background-attachment: scroll;
      background-position: center center;
      inset: 0;
    }
    .ey-cta__title { font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 1.3rem + 1.6vw, 2.2rem) !important; }
    .ey-cta__text { font-size: 0.92rem; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
    .ey-cta__btn { width: 100%; max-width: 320px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    .ey-cta { padding: 2.5rem 0; }
    .ey-cta__title { font-size: 1.5rem !important; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ey-cta__bg { background-attachment: scroll; }
    .ey-cta__btn { transition: none; }
  }
</style>
